</ul>
<h2>Market Challenges and Solutions</h2>
<p>Despite the growth prospects, the outdoor security camera market faces several challenges:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Supply Chain Disruptions:</strong> Global shortages and geopolitical tensions can affect the availability of components. Companies are diversifying suppliers and investing in local manufacturing to mitigate risks.</li>
<li><strong>Pricing Pressures:</strong> Intense competition leads to price reductions, impacting profit margins. Firms are focusing on value-added features and premium offerings to maintain profitability.</li>
